ing the scene, highlighting the pieces from the edge, shuffling the remaining pieces, previewing the scene.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712420/extras/51ba06d0e28d9f867023de11a761e3d3.avif?t=1641567122\" width=600 height=81 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Complete the puzzle and unlock the downloadable image.<br></li><li> Use it as your desktop background to inspire your day!<br></li><li> Play if you love cute animals or love puzzles ❤! </li></ul>",
